---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import { SITE } from "../config.ts";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Money Journey handles your data. Short version: we keep almost none of it." path="/privacy">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Last updated: June 2026</p>
    <div class="prose-money mt-6">
      <p>
        <strong>The short version:</strong> our calculators run entirely in your
        browser. The numbers you type are never sent to us or stored on a server.
      </p>

      <h2>Information we do not collect</h2>
      <p>
        We do not require an account, and we do not ask for your name, email, or
        any financial details to use the calculators. Anything you enter into a
        calculator stays on your device.
      </p>

      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We may use privacy-respecting analytics to understand which pages are
        popular and how the site performs. Where possible we use cookieless
        analytics that do not track individuals across sites. Aggregate data (like
        total page views) helps us improve the tools.
      </p>

      <h2>Advertising &amp; affiliate partners</h2>
      <p>
        If advertising is enabled, third-party ad networks (such as Google
        AdSense) may use cookies or similar technologies to serve and measure ads.
        These partners operate under their own privacy policies. You can usually
        manage ad personalization through your browser settings or the ad
        network's preferences page. When you click an affiliate link, the partner
        site may set its own cookies to attribute the referral.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        The core site does not require cookies to function. Any cookies present
        come from optional analytics or advertising partners as described above.
      </p>

      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <p>
        You can block cookies and third-party scripts in your browser at any time;
        the calculators will still work. You can also use private/incognito mode.
      </p>

      <h2>Children</h2>
      <p>This site is intended for adults and is not directed at children under 13.</p>

      <h2>Changes &amp; contact</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy as the site evolves. Questions? Email
        <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
